  "abstract": "Developed by ICRISAT, the Multi-Crop Millet Planter is a field-validated mechanization prototype designed to address the diverse sowing requirements of small and medium holders across dryland systems. The implement enables precise, efficient, and residue-friendly planting across a wide range of crops under both conventional and conservation agriculture.",
